Paper: 9804177
Title: Black Holes and Superconformal Mechanics
Authors: P. Claus and M. Derix and R. Kallosh and J. Kumar and P. K. Townsend and A. Van Proeyen
Abstract: The dynamics of a (super)particle near the horizon of an extreme Reissner-Nordstrom black hole is shown to be governed by an action that reduces to a (super)conformal mechanics model in the limit of large black hole mass.
